summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of following described property: Beginning at a point which bears south 89'55'02" west 416.56' and south 0-59'52" west 30' from the northeast corner of northwest quarter of the northeast quarter of Section 28 twp 26 north, range 4 east W. M.; thence running south 0'59' 52" West 631.46', thence north 89'00'02" east 110.02' to point of beginning being designated at Tract A Homewood Park according to plat thereof recorded in volume 22 of plats, page 73 records of King County, Washington; with respect to Use Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto one new section numbered 2-360.
